verse_text: v 42 inji eyi wukutwesha kumwila manakweyi ngahi neyi eyi manakwami tali nikutumbuli kachibalu kanalakumukili mujisu jeyi hakwila ipulanga jiji mujisu jeyeyi aweni hiwunajilukuku eyi mfwikizhi sambilaku kufumisha ipulanga jiji mujisu jeyeyi aweni mwaka winzi wumoni kutumbula chachiwahi kachibalu kanalakumukili mujisu jamanakweyi

v 6 ichi jinu atufumishili kunshimbi kuyumoyu yatukakeleli tuyafu kulonda twakakalakali munzhila yayiha yoyasipilitu bayi munzhila yayikulu yanjikiliwu ichi jinu tukwakula netuji nshimbi hishinji tahinji chinzhila ilanga jinu hanaji kwiluka nshiji chakaji nshimbiku mulonga neyi nshimbi yabulili kwila nawu kwikala nalwisu chazhila hinaji kwiluka lwisuku
